#

Grilled Chicken Caesar Salad

25 min
$10
550 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

Low CarbHigh ProteinGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Salad

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuick

Description

A classic Caesar salad topped with juicy grilled chicken, crisp romaine, and a creamy dressing, perfect for a healthy meal.

Ingredients

  • romaine lettuce: 4 cups, chopped
  • grilled chicken breast: 1 large, sliced
  • parmesan cheese: 1/4 cup, shaved
  • caesar dressing: 1/2 cup
  • croutons: 1/2 cup
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
